## рџ—„пёЏ Database Schema

| Table | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `users` | App users with Telegram ID |
| `families` | Family/group with a master user |
| `family_members` | Members per family (soft-kick via `kicked_at`) |
| `wallets` | User wallets with balance tracking |
| `categories` | Transaction categories (in/out/both) |
| `transactions` | All transactions with wallet & category reference |

## рџ”’ Security

- Telegram webhook validated via `X-Telegram-Bot-Api-Secret-Token` header
- `.env` is git-ignored вЂ” never commit your tokens
- Family data isolation вЂ” kicked members' data is hidden but not deleted

